## Key Architecture Insights

**Grid Component**:
- Lightweight, composable grid with built-in keyboard nav
- Context-based approach for efficient updates to child items
- Column count is flexible (3-6 columns)
- Proper wrap-around behavior for directional keys

**SearchDropdown Component**:
- Self-contained dropdown with complete keyboard + mouse support
- Sections provide visual grouping without affecting flat option indexing
- Click-outside and Escape handling for proper closure
